Summary: looked like a jackstone... you know like the game jacks. like six balls connected together
divs: Sighting Detailsmy mom and sister were driving across the bridge on browns bridge rd. in gainesville when my sister says to my mom "look mom theres a jack in the sky, my mom sees this to. she slows down to watch as it slowly glides across the night sky and when she gets to the other side of the bridge the trees get in the way of sight. she never saw it again. upon ariving home both my mom and sister were very excited to tell me about the accurance, my mom still has the same story today it has never changed.
